&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="http://farm1.staticflickr.com/138/352972944_4f9d568680_z.jpg?zz=1"&gt;&lt;img alt="Nikola Tesla Corner by nicwest, on Flickr" class="thumbnail" src="http://farm1.staticflickr.com/138/352972944_4f9d568680.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have managed to install Nikola, and build a site using it using this code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://laurentperrinet.github.io/sciblog/listings/install-nikola.sh.html"&gt;install-nikola.sh&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://laurentperrinet.github.io/sciblog/listings/install-nikola.sh"&gt;(Source)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-1" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;git clone git://github.com/getnikola/nikola.git
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-2" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; nikola
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-3" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install -r requirements-full.txt
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-4" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install .
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-5" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;nikola init --demo invibe
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-6" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;nikola build
&lt;a id="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-7" name="rest_code_d4c625c5b6a04f359949fcde7af18356-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;nikola serve
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pretty simple, congratulations to the developpers!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More info:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can read the manual &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://getnikola.com/handbook.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can see a demo photo gallery &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://laurentperrinet.github.io/sciblog/galleries/demo/index.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can learn more about Nikola at &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://getnikola.com"&gt;http://getnikola.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
